HEADWORD: Undeeded
<hw>Un*deed"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
deeded or transferred by deed; <as>as, <ex>undeeded</ex>
land</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not made famous by any great action.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undefatigable</ent>⟦br⟧
